{"tid":2506427,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"法國學者：中華文化靠征服和吞併來前進，從不平等對待他人","createTime":"2021-04-27T10:00:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T14:18:04.000Z","uid":276716,"like":71,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"fb78574f8403cb85790f6367082dd01e95673233","tid":2506427,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:00:46.000Z","msg":"全文連結：<a href=\"https://hmssulphur.blogspot.com/2021/04/blog-post_27.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhmssulphur.blogspot.com%2F2021%2F04%2Fblog-post_27.html%3Fm%3D1&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oFDApO%2Br9QW7Zx2priNtVuo%3D&h=1dd60664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hmssulphur.blogspot.com/2021/04/blog-post_27.html?m=1</a><br />\n更多內容：<a href=\"https://mewe.com/join/scshistory\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fjoin%2Fscshistory&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oFDApO%2Br9QW7Zx2priNtVuo%3D&h=0625a5ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/join/scshistory</a><br />\n<br />\n以南中國海為中心，四周被陸地包圍所形成的區域，一些學者比擬為亞洲的地中海。海域北方是華南，接壤亞洲大陸，南方則是諸多群島和半島，通向印度洋。專攻東南亞研究的Wilhelm Solheim和諸位學者都認為，這片海域組成一個東南亞文化區，華南亦是當中一環。<br />\n<br />\n「的確，這樣做（把廣東和廣西納入東南亞）不無道理。華夏人不過在秦王朝和西漢王朝才控制此處，而且直至今天這裡的習俗、語言和生境，仍然接近它南邊的土地遠多於「中原」⋯⋯因此我會破釜沉舟，把雲南平原和嶺南包括在東南亞之內。」&mdash;&mdash;《The Bronze Age of Southeast Asia》<br />\n<br />\n公元之後，印度和本土文化結合的果實在海域南方造就一系列繁榮城邦，例如占婆、吳哥、馬六甲。反觀北岸卻陷入中華帝國的郡縣化統治之中。<br />\n<br />\n放眼南方諸多半島和群島，後來稱為東南亞或印度支那之處，印度古典文化無遠弗屆，滲透到每個島嶼。雖然與中華帝國有悠久的朝貢關係，為何中華文化和制度長期止步於紅河三角洲，沒有更大影響呢？法國學者George Coed&egrave;s探討過當中原因。<br />\n<br />\nCoed&egrave;s比較了印度和中華，認為兩者的殖民方式有很大差異。中華依賴軍事力量去輸出文化，強迫本地人跟從自己的習慣。「被中國軍事征服的諸國，都必須複製中國的官僚、習俗、宗教、語言、文字」<br />\n<br />\n「中國人靠征服和吞併來前進，士兵佔據別國，官員散播中華文化。」這雖然把中華文化傳播到海洋北岸，卻只局限於帝國武力所及的範圍內。<br />\n<br />\n而印度恰恰相反，以顧問方式推行印度文化，同時相當尊重各地原有習俗。這種方法不費一兵一卒，卻隨著貿易路線滲透到南中國海各處。<br />\n<br />\n印度本土與海外的印度化王國，是平等關係，而非中華那種朝貢關係。「孟加拉灣兩岸在對等基礎上互換使節，而中華總是要求『南蠻』定期朝貢，承認自己的宗主權」<br />\n<br />\n印度平等開放的態度，促進了文化傳播，同時讓各地保持自己特色。高綿、占婆、爪哇諸邦組成繁榮的古典印度化世界。<br />\n<br />\n這種政治模式，學者用「曼陀羅模型」來描述，類似西歐的封建體系。將來有機會再介紹曼陀羅模式如何在印支半島和印尼群島大放異彩。"},{"pid":"6681cf179e2dabce693ec336ce4313552ca0aadf","tid":2506427,"uid":276716,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:01:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZtpw8h8tJ5D3ELKu1aB7M8Xs3yhEhLhSeUpBeBrYE9kY?filename=Uv1BGBN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUv1BGBN.jpg&h=5dba8fb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南中國海地區構成一個自成一體的文化區域"},{"pid":"8558f14113b29d85f370db41840d55370ac8af02","tid":2506427,"uid":69866,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:01:46.000Z","msg":"法國學者：mon is woman"},{"pid":"5f2d6f18898d4626d6336d384ef5ded8d0ee9d24","tid":2506427,"uid":276716,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:02:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTpKNbEjszMC6x1HztmtXP16WxWb788fuBU3sauLNUDpz?filename=jp3AcJC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjp3AcJC.jpg&h=13af4cd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n法國的東方學家George Coed&egrave;s長年從事東南亞研究，聲譽極高。他認為歷史上中華文化在東南亞的吸引力遠不及印度文化，只能依靠軍事武力的專制方式強迫其他人接受自己。"},{"pid":"265e6397374e68c254b920ad2b482ec92daf645e","tid":2506427,"uid":118346,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:03:24.000Z","msg":"印度恰恰相反，以<span class=\"red\">顧問方式推行印度文化，同時相當尊重各地原有習俗</span>。這種方法不費一兵一卒，卻隨著貿易路線滲透到南中國海各處 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd7d66b3e9bd5c2fb1ac00a571b41fbc3e580e2","tid":2506427,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:13:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qma4qbjnoFDRenuvgwSwYQ6JiSPTZwQg5ZFJgarbfaETHh?filename=P1ZDay0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP1ZDay0.jpg&h=ff6fda52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中華文化透過軍事武力擴展自己影響力。在此之前，東南亞的文化分佈可能如圖所示。"},{"pid":"d367aa2e573759d882b9dfcd1f36e218f7075143","tid":2506427,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:14:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYi1JQoqPNLSJGxGLLb37GgDvixfmPvYcAfbMS4JSiGGU?filename=ti0Cq7L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fti0Cq7L.jpg&h=597185c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印度不曾軍事入侵，但其思想與東南亞本土文化結合後，滋養出極為富饒豐腴的文明。"},{"pid":"d233be46d08f7fdfc0c6c7533fe15ac1ece63973","tid":2506427,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:14:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTN5Pz4QZMCVsAW28qtDvALXVHowuAypYTdJ5N3wZWE3N?filename=KmYo57V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKmYo57V.png&h=5a40d6bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曼陀羅模型描述了東南亞在古典時代的國際秩序，有別於東亞大陸的「普天之下莫非王土」。在此模型下，東南亞非常繁榮富裕。"},{"pid":"3932c08c9780713855c74d66221a49a9f395394a","tid":2506427,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:15:15.000Z","msg":"參考：<br />\n<br />\n1. Coed&egrave;s, G. (1968) The Indianized States of Southeast Asia. Australian National University Press<br />\n<br />\n2. Higham, C. (1996) The Bronze Age of Southeast Asia. Cambridge World Archeology<br />\n<br />\n3. <a href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Li-Jin-66/publication/6171756_Mitochondrial_DNA_diversity_and_population_differentiation_in_Southern_East_Asia/links/5c5b8e2145851582c3d3d8c0/Mitochondrial-DNA-diversity-and-population-differentiation-in-Southern-East-Asia.pdf?origin=publication_detail\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fprofile%2FLi-Jin-66%2Fpublication%2F6171756_Mitochondrial_DNA_diversity_and_population_differentiation_in_Southern_East_Asia%2Flinks%2F5c5b8e2145851582c3d3d8c0%2FMitochondrial-DNA-diversity-and-population-differentiation-in-Southern-East-Asia.pdf%3Forigin%3Dpublication_detail&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oFDApO%2Br9QW7Zx2priNtVuo%3D&h=552